title: UV-Bundle: Avoid Russian Internet Censorship (2013) RUS
description:
UV-Bundle "Fuck The Bear Edition", contains:


Tor (including Vidalia)
Portable Firefox (NOT Tor Browser, full Firefox with flash, history, etc. instead)
Portable uTorrent pre-tuned for making announces via TOR socks proxy.

and intended for Russian users who wants to access sites, blocked by "Roskomnadzor", including various Russian torrent trackers and warez portals, as well as politic sites.
